Package: HealthMarkers
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Clinical, Metabolic, and Cardiovascular Biomarker Calculations
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sufyan", family = "Suleman",
           email = "sufyansuleman@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6612-6915"))
Description: Computes over 50 specialist health marker functions covering
    insulin sensitivity and resistance indices (fasting, oral glucose
    tolerance test, adipose-tissue, tracer, and DXA-based), glycaemic and
    lipid markers, atherogenic and metabolic syndrome scores, liver
    steatosis and fibrosis scores, and cardiovascular risk algorithms
    (Framingham, ASCVD, QRISK3, SCORE2/SCORE2-OP). Also implements renal
    function (eGFR, KFRE, CKD staging), pulmonary function (spirometry
    z-scores, BODE index), inflammatory markers and aging clocks (iAge),
    hormonal panels, body composition and anthropometric z-scores, bone
    turnover markers and fracture risk (FRAX), frailty and comorbidity
    indices (Rockwood, Charlson), psychiatric rating scales, and biomarker
    panels from alternative biofluids (urine, saliva, sweat). Missing value
    imputation helpers and a unified 'all_health_markers()' dispatcher that
    returns all requested marker groups as a single wide tibble are included.
